    <item>
      <title>泰国将俄罗斯人免签居留期限延长至七月以促进旅游业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/thailand-extends-longer-visa-free-stay-for-russians-until-july-to-boost-tourism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国内阁批准了一项计划，允许免签证进入该国的俄罗斯游客最多停留两个月，因为这个东南亚国家押注于旅游业以支持经济复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/thailand-extends-longer-visa-free-stay-for-russians-until-july-to-boost-tourism</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:31:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>玻利维亚的繁荣已转向萧条，助长了总统不太可能的东山再起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-23/bolivia-s-dollar-crisis-pits-evo-morales-against-luis-arce-as-election-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路易斯·阿尔塞总统对抑制通货膨胀感到自豪。但一场酝酿已久的金融危机使这一标志性成就面临风险，可能为他从导师转型为竞争对手的埃沃·莫拉莱斯(Evo Morales)开辟道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-23/bolivia-s-dollar-crisis-pits-evo-morales-against-luis-arce-as-election-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:00:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
